% SDEG CLUSTER BOOTSTRAP PLOTS
%
%---------------------------------------------------------------------
<<rp_pvclust_hcl_plot,out.width="1.0\\textwidth",fig.cap=paste('Co-expressed gene cluster dendrogram with bootstrap probabilities (RP, ',DendrLabls,'). The y axis shows the distance at which clusters were formed by the complete linkage clustering algorithm based on uncentered Pearson correlation distance between \\logtwo fold changes. Multiscale bootstrap probabilities are shown at each branch intersection. Significant clusters are highlighted in blue. Asterisks indicate genes that were significantly expressed at a certain day.',sep='')>>=
